{
  "text": "Was it necessary for them to have a unified social complex for these visitations to occur? What conditions were nec— I'm saying, what conditions were necessary for these visitations to occur? I am Ra. The conditions were two: the calling of a group of people whose square overcame the integrated resistance of those unwilling to search or learn; the second requirement, the relative naïveté of those members of the Confederation who felt that direct transfer of information would necessarily be as helpful for Atlanteans as it had been for the Confederation entity.",
